social_posts.post_text: A dream come true. Thank you @chet__lo for giving me the honor of opening your show. You light up the room with your personality and we all appreciate how much you care about your models and what you do 💓💓💓thank you @yagamoto for your words of guidence. First show in London down 😭
Thank you @_pronounce for having me. Music was 🔥🔥🔥🫶🏽

London fashion week ✔️ Thank you @paulandjoeparis for having me. 🌻🌻 London has been amazing. Thank you to all the teams who were envolved and to my amazing @chaptermgmt family who worked their butts off.
Happy that my first ever Paris show was with this team. You guys made me feel amazing. Merciiiii 🥰🥰🌹🌹🌹Thank you @situationist_official for having me and thank you for these two beautiful moments.

What a wild ride this last month has been. Feeling so grateful and in alignment. Walked my first shows in London and Paris, opened a show, shot a campaign, ate my way through Pari, shot another amazing editorial with my boo thang @beauteousmax 🌹got to meet so many internet friends and heads of brands I love so much IRL, and got blessed with a beautiful new neck piece by @dj__peanut ⚡️So much love to all the teams who rocked with me and to anyone who gave me an encouraging word during all the ups and downs this month. Thank you to my agencies who pushed me this season. ♥️♥️♥️🤸🏽‍♀️10 slides is not enough to wrap up this month but we try.

So @edmaximus and I have been experimenting with AI for quite a while now, slowly injecting it into all our work together. One thing I find funny is that the fashion world has mostly used AI as a way to create/do the same type of editorials/jobs that us models and creatives do everyday. That shouldn’t be the point of AI. I’ve also had a lot of conversations with friends about what it means for the future. It should help expand our imagination when it comes to what we would have once thought impossible to get from a picture.. eventually video. It should be fun! Sometimes I hope what we come up with exists in some alternative universe, a better one. For now we create our own. My planet is Babino. My little world of Fairies, faeries, nymphs and soon to be human spider hybrids. Hope you enjoy our project @spectrachromatica, follow for more in depth descriptions 🥰🦾
Trying to come up with a caption (and anxiety) sometimes stops me from posting all together. Sometimes it’s just for the fit or the moment. 🌝

Another year 🎂🎈on this spinning ball of beauty. So thankful to @edmaximus for this surprise trip to Cartagena🇨🇴. I welcome all this next year has in store for me. This one has been insane in the best way. A lot of firsts. I’ve started so many new passions, ended a lot of unfulfilling personal relationships, and finally let fear stop holding me back. Grateful to my tribe, close and afar, for the love that you guys continue to pour into me. ❤️❤️♥️ I cannot wait to come back here.
Colombia phone dump. 💃🏽🎈♥️
Halloween will always be my favorite holiday 🎃💀 @edmaximus and I decided to do a full shoot this year using ai to make it more fantastical.
Never needed a trip more. Got to see my best friend, all of my loved ones, and get to know family I haven’t seen since I was a kid. Cherry on top is Dad is now hitched. 💍🤵🏽‍♀️

This year has meant so much to me. Lots of ugly growth, firsts, and insane accomplishments. Switching shit up in 2024. Love all you beautiful humans in my life, you give me so much strength. Also this reel took an embarrassing amount of time to do. Fun tho 🧚🏽‍♀️🧚🏽‍♀️
